'''Shahriyar Moghanlou''' ({{langx|fa|شهريار مغانلو}}; born 21 December 1994) is an Iranian professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)#Centre-forward|centre-forward]] for [[UAE Pro League]] club [[Kalba FC|Kalba]] and the [[Iran national football team|Iran national team]].

==Club career==
Shahriyar was born in the city of [[Zanjan, Iran|Zanjan]] to an [[Iranian Azerbaijani]] family. Moghanlou started his professional career with [[Paykan F.C.|Paykan]] while he promoted to the first team in the winter of 2015. He made his professional debut for Paykan against [[Gostaresh Foulad F.C.|Gostaresh Foulad]] on 4 February 2015 when he was used as a substitute for [[Ali Hosseini]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/shahriar-moghanlou/395745/|title=Iran - S. Moghanlou - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://iranleague.ir/MatchDetails/6408|title = سازمان لیگ فوتبال ایران}}</ref>

===Santa Clara===
On 23 September 2020, Moghanlou signed a three-year contract with Portuguese [[Primeira Liga]] side [[C.D. Santa Clara|Santa Clara]].<ref>{{cite web |title=OFFICIAL: SHAHRYIAR MOGHANLOU |url=https://cdsantaclara.com/oficial-shahriar-moghanlou/ |publisher=C.D. Santa Clara |date=23 September 2020}}</ref>

===Persepolis===
On 7 March 2021, Moghanlou signed a contract with [[Persian Gulf Pro League]] champions [[Persepolis F.C.|Persepolis]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|date=2021-03-07|title=Persepolis complete signing of Shahriyar Moghanlou|url=https://www.tehrantimes.com/news/458897/Persepolis-complete-signing-of-Shahriyar-Moghanlou|access-date=2021-03-08|website=Tehran Times|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-03-07|title=شهریار مغانلو به پرسپولیس پیوست|url=https://www.isna.ir/news/99121713070/شهریار-مغانلو-به-پرسپولیس-پیوست|access-date=2021-03-08|website=ایسنا|language=fa}}</ref> The details of the fee contract have not been released.<ref name=":0" />

==International career==
He made his senior debut on 23 March 2023 against [[Russia national football team|Russia]] in a friendly match.

He scored his first international goal on 12 September 2023 against [[Angola national football team|Angola]] in a friendly match.

