==Personal life==
On 3 January 2026, Moghanloo publicly supported the [[2025–2026 Iranian protests]], stating: "We are doing the hardest thing in the world because we are both sad and hopeful. We are both homesick and full of hope. We are both tired and full of struggle to live."<ref>https://www.iranintl.com/202601034038</ref>

